Harby End Table.description:
The Harby collection captures the nostalgic look and feel of a 19th century work table. Made of tongue and groove planks harvested from stocks of reclaimed wood pallets, each piece bears an authentic combination of stains, saw marks, dents, pits and nail holes only found in salvaged materials. Offering more than just a great silhouette, this group's trestle-reinforced sawhorse base is engineered for superior stability and strength.
- Built from solid Pine sourced from reclaimed shipping pallets.
- Rustic Tawny finish.
- Natural color variance between planks and wood species ensures each piece is one of a kind.
- Matte NC lacquer finish seals the wood surface while maintaining its rustic character.

Townsend End Table.description:
The rough and tumble Townsend collection  is crafted from solid hardwood, featuring naturally roughhewn planks with heavy saw marks, pitting and wane.  A 9-step finish uses glaze to highlight wood grain and a light wash to simulate the patina of age. 
- Full-extension ball bearing drawer glides.
- Open storage.
- Java finish.

Reese End Table.description:
Made from 2-inch thick planks of solid Acacia wood and powder-coated iron, the Reese collection's table top is finished and sealed with a clear semi-gloss NC lacquer to preserve its genuine tree edges and unique wood grain. The nature of the wood and live edges ensures each table is one-of-a-kind, with random edge profiles, knots, cracks and varied grain patterns shining through sundry hues of amber and golden brown.
- Top constructed from 2-inch thick solid Acacia planks with natural live edges.
- Legs constructed from iron tube with a satin black powder coat.
- Natural Acacia semi-gloss finish.
- Live edges are sanded and sealed for a beautiful, splinter-free finish.
- Natural variations in the wood grain and edge pattern ensure no two pieces are alike.
- Handmade by skilled artisans in India.

Peekaboo End Table.description:
Journey into the world of organic modern with the Peekaboo collection from Modus Furniture. Featuring a 2-inch thick natural live-edge solid Acacia top with a pull-through acrylic base, this collection showcases an unexpected combination of manmade and natural materials. 
- Constructed from 2-inch thick planks of solid Acacia wood with natural live edges.
- Natural Acacia semi-gloss finish.
- Live edges can vary significantly in shape and appearance, with visible knots, cracks and grain patterns, ensuring the one of a kind nature of each piece.
- Base constructed from solid acrylic with a Mohs hardness rating of 5.
- Handmade by skilled artisans in India.

Cally End Table.description:
With graceful curves, modern sensibility and functional appeal, the Cally collection provides an updated take on classic farmhouse style. Crafted entirely from solid pine, rough-hewn planks bear the characteristic saw marks, dents, pits, and random knots of freshly-milled timber. A rugged yet refined Antique Mocha finish uses a rustic glaze to simulate the patina of weathered lumber and a lacquer top coat to showcase the rich natural character of the wood.  
- Built from solid Pine.
- Antique Mocha finish.
- Cross-banded breadboard top panels.
- Open storage.

Craster End Table.description:
Touched by the marks of time, our Craster collection is a rugged homage to classic farmhouse design. Its roughhewn planks are harvested from stocks of reclaimed wood bearing a unique combination of saw marks, gouges, dents, pits and nail holes that differ with each piece.  Natural knot and grain patterns are sealed to perfection with a rich Smoky Taupe finish.

Jackson End Table.description:
An easy fit with any style, the Jackson collection provides a versatile solution to everyday living needs. The box frame coffee table can be used alone or adjacent to one or both halves of the round end table to create a variety of shapes and sizes. End tables can be used individually as small semi-circular tables or together as an ample round.  
- Made from New Pine with tongue and groove joinery.
- Heavily distressed surface includes natural saw marks and pits from the milling process.
- Unique finishing process uses a dark base coat and a light gray top coat with sand-through to focus attention on the unique rustic texture of the lumber.
- Weathered gray finish adds a casual feel to your space.

Lyon End Table.description:
Set on a midcentury-style tripod base, the Lyon collection boasts a sophisticated fiber-reinforced gray concrete table top that gives it a modern, minimalist quality without the heavy lifting. Each cement top is hand-poured and finished with a clear wax sealant to create a natural, authentically industrial look.  
- Fiber-reinforced concrete (FRC) table top has the natural look and feel of concrete with less permeability and improved impact/abrasion resistance.
- One-piece base consists of tubular steel legs welded to curved solid steel stretchers in a brushed bronze finish.
- Semi-porous wax finish over natural concrete - unattended spills may leave stains.
- Hand-brushed, powder-coated metal finish.
- Assembly required.

Yosemite End Table.description:

Rough-hewn planks crafted entirely from solid pine bear the characteristic saw marks, dents, pits, and random knots of logs milled on the steam-powered circular and sash saws of the era. A rustic black pine finish balances transparency and opacity to showcase these natural imperfections.  
- Made from solid Pine.
- Exposed bolts and rustic cross-bracing.
- Mortise and tenon framing and tongue and groove table top.

Thick planks of solid Pine are hewn by skilled artisans and joined using mortise and tenon framing and breadboard ends. Each piece is hand-sanded and finished to create a rugged-yet-smooth texture that will last for generations.
- Built from solid Acacia wood in a Rustic Grey finish.
- Powder-coated industrial metal drawer pulls.
- Drawers mounted on full-extension ball bearing glides.

Adler Nightstand.description:
Mid-century style takes a contemporary detour with the Adler collection by Modus Furniture. With a simple yet sophisticated profile, Adler is built from Walnut veneers in a knotty walnut finish. Bronzed brass campaign-style corner brackets and tapered metal legs provide a subtle contrast to the warm tones of the timber for a look that is both fresh and timeless.
- Made from Walnut veneers.
- Bronzed brass corner brackets, bases, and cup drawer pulls.
- Full-extension ball bearing drawer glides.
- Sanded and stained drawer interiors with English dovetail joinery.

Nevis Nightstand.description:
Crafted from Tropical Mahogany solids and a variety of beautiful veneers, the Nevis collection is a foundational American classic. Stained in a rich Espresso tone, this group offers a vast array of platform, low-profile and sleigh bed options for looks that are both sleek and functional. 
- Full-extension ball bearing drawer glides.
- Sanded and stained drawer interiors with English dovetail joinery.

Montana Nightstand.description:
Add a modern edge to your space with the Montana collection by Modus Furniture. Varying in hue from blonde to nutty brown, rustic planks of solid wood are lightly sanded to allow natural saw marks, pits, knots and grain patterns to shine through. Crisp white frames balance this timeworn aesthetic for an altogether show-stopping look. 
- Solid Sengon Tekik features a rich, contrasting grain.
- Flush-mount bronze drawer pulls.
- Full-extension ball bearing drawer glides.

Brighton Nightstand with Charging Stati.description:
The Brighton collection is expertly crafted from Tropical Mahogany solids and Cherry Veneers and features a refined American finish in a deep, vibrant Cinnamon. When combined with the Brighton wood and sleigh beds, this collection will fill your bedroom with understated splendor and luxury.
- In-drawer charging station provides convenient, clutter-free charging for mobile devices.
- Drawers feature French and English dovetail joinery as well as corner blocking for rigidity and durability, and full-extension ball bearing glides. 
- Satin nickel finished handles.

Portland Nightstand.description:
Transitional in design but modern in appearance, the Portland collection adds subtle details and heavy solid wood construction to a Bauhaus-like form.  Each piece sits atop a recessed base with thick splayed legs and is finished in a smooth, low-sheen walnut stain for a timeless, substantial effect. 
- Crafted from solid butcher block Acacia wood.
- Asymmetrical, integrated drawer pulls are cut in a rounded rectangle shape and accented with oil rubbed bronze metal backings.
- Drawers are mounted on full-extension ball bearing glides and are constructed with sanded, stained and dovetailed drawer boxes.

City II Nightstand.description:
Featuring an all-new Basalt Grey finish and Dolphin linen upholstery, the City II collection is a timeless classic that emphasizes authentic livability. Built from Mahogany solid wood and veneer, signature features include beveled solid wood drawer fronts, floating tops, gently sleighed, padded headboards, and shallow top drawers for storing delicate items..
- Wire brushed basalt gray finish .
- 100% polyester linen upholstery in Marlow/dolphin fabric .
- Sanded and stained solid wood drawer boxes with English dovetail joinery. .
- Full-extension ball bearing drawer glides .
- Felt-lined dresser and chest top drawers .
- Discrete metal-to-metal bed rail fittings for easy assembly and long-term durability.

Yosemite Blanket Box.description:
The Yosemite collection recreates the improvised, utilitarian look of early 20th century factory furniture. Crafted entirely from solid wood, this collection utilizes mortise and tenon frames, tongue and groove tops, and frame and panel sides for strength and durability. Roughhewn planks bear the characteristic saw marks, dents, pits, and random knots of logs milled on the steam powered circular and sash saws of the era. Finally, a rustic black pine finish balances transparency and opacity to showcase imperfections inherent in the timber.  
- Exposed bolts and hammered metal drawer pulls.
- Full-extension ball bearing drawer glides.

Constructed from quality wooden frames, this group features center leg supports and discreet metal-to-metal siderail brackets for ultimate stability and comfort.  Wood components are stained in a versatile Chocolate finish to match with a wide range of modern wood tones.  
- Ready-to-assemble headboard post.
- Solid wood legs.
- Hook-on bed rail fittings.
- Thick padded headboard features discreet vertical seams.

Royal Storage Bed.description:
Indulgent tufting and cushioning surround you in luxury with the Geneva upholstered bed collection from Modus Furniture.  Available as headboards or complete beds, each model is wrapped from head to toe in a textural linen fabric for a tailored finish. With styles ranging from sleek and modern to lavishly hand tufted, this collection features hand-hammered nails, high arching curves and piped edges that highlight each angle and shape.
- European-style bentwood platform mattress support designed for use without a box spring. 
- Front-facing storage drawers are mounted on full-extension ball bearing drawer glides and are supported by metal casters.

Simple Platform Bed.description:
Crafted from Tropical Mahogany solids and a variety of beautiful veneers, the Nevis collection is a foundational American classic. Stained in a rich Espresso tone, this group offers a vast array of platform, low-profile and sleigh bed options for looks that are both sleek and functional. 
- Platform bed slat system designed for use without a box spring.

Adler Bed.description:
Mid-century style takes a contemporary detour with the Adler collection by Modus Furniture. With a simple yet sophisticated profile, Adler is built from Walnut veneers in a knotty walnut finish. Bronzed brass campaign-style corner brackets and tapered metal legs provide a subtle contrast to the warm tones of the timber for a look that is both fresh and timeless.
- Made from Walnut veneers.
- Bronzed brass corner brackets and base.
- Shows well with mattresses of any height; box spring required.

- Platform bed slat system designed for use without a box spring.

Figura Simple Platform Bed.description:
Clean contemporary makes a comeback with the Figura collection. Available as headboards, platform frames or complete beds, this collection's casual style is rooted in simple design paired with Mahogany lumber. Headboards offer a modern take on three classic silhouettes, while the platform bed frame is anchored by heavy solid wood block legs. Offered in a lustrous Chocolate Brown finish.  
- Constructed from Mahogany solid wood and Mahogany wood veneer.
- Semi-gloss chocolate brown finish with NC lacquer top coat
- Heavy solid wood block legs.
- Headboards fit standard metal frames with threaded inserts at 5 5/8, 6 1/4, 8 1/8 and 8 3/4 above floor level.  Headboards attach to most non-standard metal frames with a Modi-plate (available from metal frame manufacturer).
- Platform frame designed for use without a box spring.
- Display racks available.

Meadow Platform bed.description:
The Meadow collection is rugged durability and contemporary styling defined. Crafted from solid Acacia, its sleek lines showcase naturally occurring knot, grain and color variations inherent to the timber. Rustic wire brushing and a heavily glazed Brick Brown finish result in a perfect balance between modern and rustic. 
- Platform bed slat systems designed for use without a box spring.

Element Platform Bed.description:
Bring the beauty and structure of clean architecture to your bedroom with the Element collection. Thick miter-jointed outer posts are the focus of this group, whose streamlined aesthetic stretches from the top panels all the way to the floor.  Tropical Mahogany solid wood and Mahogany wood veneers are finished in a dark chocolate brown with tones ranging from dark to golden brown and burgundy.  
- High picture-framed headboard panel showcases geometric square insets. 
- Premium-quality metal-to-metal hardware.
- Platform bed slat system designed for use without a box spring.

Yosemite Dresser.description:
The Yosemite collection recreates the improvised, utilitarian look of early 20th century factory furniture. Crafted entirely from solid wood, this collection utilizes mortise and tenon frames, tongue and groove tops, and frame and panel sides for strength and durability. Roughhewn planks bear the characteristic saw marks, dents, pits, and random knots of logs milled on the steam powered circular and sash saws of the era. Finally, a rustic black pine finish balances transparency and opacity to showcase imperfections inherent in the timber.  
- Exposed bolts and hammered metal drawer pulls.
- Full-extension ball bearing drawer glides.
- Felt-lined top drawers.
- Sanded and stained hardwood drawer boxes with English dovetail corners.

Meadow Dresser.description:

Crafted from solid Acacia, its sleek lines showcase naturally occurring knot, grain and color variations inherent to the timber. - Solid Acacia fronts, tops and sides; plywood backs, drawer boxes, dust covers and bed slats.
- Exposed mortise and tenon corner joints.
- Full-extension ball bearing drawer glides.
- Sanded and stained drawer interiors with English dovetail joinery.
- Felt-lined top drawers.

Brighton Dresser.description:
The Brighton collection is expertly crafted from Tropical Mahogany solids and Cherry Veneers and features a refined American finish in a deep, vibrant Cinnamon. When combined with the Brighton wood and sleigh beds, this collection will fill your bedroom with understated splendor and luxury.
- Felt-lined top drawers. 
- Drawers feature French and English dovetail joinery as well as corner blocking for rigidity and durability, and full-extension ball bearing glides. 
- Satin nickel finished handles.

City II Dresser.description:
Featuring an all-new Basalt Grey finish and Dolphin linen upholstery, the City II collection is a timeless classic that emphasizes authentic livability. Built from Mahogany solid wood and veneer, signature features include beveled solid wood drawer fronts, floating tops, gently sleighed, padded headboards, and shallow top drawers for storing delicate items..
- Wire brushed basalt gray finish .
- 100% polyester linen upholstery in Marlow/dolphin fabric .
- Sanded and stained solid wood drawer boxes with English dovetail joinery. .
- Full-extension ball bearing drawer glides .
- Felt-lined dresser and chest top drawers .
- Discrete metal-to-metal bed rail fittings for easy assembly and long-term durability.

Montana Dresser.description:
Add a modern edge to your space with the Montana collection by Modus Furniture. Varying in hue from blonde to nutty brown, rustic planks of solid wood are lightly sanded to allow natural saw marks, pits, knots and grain patterns to shine through. Crisp white frames balance this timeworn aesthetic for an altogether show-stopping look. 
- Solid Sengon Tekik features a rich, contrasting grain.
- Flush-mount bronze drawer pulls.
- Felt-lined top drawers. 
- Full-extension ball bearing drawer glides.

Nevis Dresser.description:
Crafted from Tropical Mahogany solids and a variety of beautiful veneers, the Nevis collection is a foundational American classic. Stained in a rich Espresso tone, this group offers a vast array of platform, low-profile and sleigh bed options for looks that are both sleek and functional. 
- Removable felt lining in the top drawers .
- Full-extension ball bearing drawer glides.

Element Dresser.description:

Thick miter-jointed outer posts are the focus of this group, whose streamlined aesthetic stretches from the top panels all the way to the floor.  Tropical Mahogany solid wood and Mahogany wood veneers are finished in a dark chocolate brown with tones ranging from dark to golden brown and burgundy.  
- Carved drawer pulls run the length of each drawer.
- Full-extension ball bearing drawer glides on sanded and stained solid wood drawer boxes with front/rear English dovetail joinery. 
- Felt-lined top drawers.

Portland Dresser.description:
Transitional in design but modern in appearance, the Portland collection adds subtle details and heavy solid wood construction to a Bauhaus-like form.  Each piece sits atop a recessed base with thick splayed legs and is finished in a smooth, low-sheen walnut stain for a timeless, substantial effect. 
- Crafted from solid butcher block Acacia wood.
- Asymmetrical, integrated drawer pulls are cut in a rounded rectangle shape and accented with oil rubbed bronze metal backings.
- Drawers are mounted on full-extension ball bearing glides and are constructed with sanded, stained and dovetailed drawer boxes.

Riva Dresser.description:
The Riva bedroom collection offers styling and design that will add a sleek modern look to your bedroom. This collection is crafted from Tropical Mahogany solid wood and Birch wood veneer in a chocolate brown finish with highlights ranging in hue from yellow to burgundy.
- Full-extension ball bearing drawer glides with English dovetail joinery.
- Sanded & stained solid wood drawer boxes.
- Lustrous chrome drawer pulls.

Paragon Dresser.description:
Get a fresh take on classic Shaker style with the Paragon bedroom from Modus Furniture. Crafted entirely from solid Mahogany in an opaque black finish, this group features a simple, framed panel design with reverse bevel floating tops. Casegoods rest atop tapered legs with a gently arched lower side cross.
- Sanded and stained solid wood drawer boxes with English dovetail joinery.
- Full-extension ball bearing drawer glides.
- Felt-lined top drawers for storing delicate items.

Ocean Dresser.description:
Inspired by modern California beach-chic, the Ocean collection is crafted from solid Sengon Tekik wood in a vibrant natural finish. Distinctive wave fronts provide the perfect canvas for hidden drawer pulls, which maintain the group's clean profile. Breathe fresh air into your bedroom with Ocean.
- Made from Sengon Tekik wood in a natural finish.
- Hidden pulls routed under each drawer front.
- Removable felt lining in the top drawers.
- Full-extension ball bearing drawer glides.
- Sanded and stained drawer interiors with English dovetail joinery.

Austin Chesser.description:
Inspired by the charm and DIY spirit of old-world agrarian living, Austin provides a modern interpretation of classic farmhouse design. This collection's craftsmanship shows in the details: thick planks of solid Pine are painstakingly hewn by skilled artisans and joined with a combination of mortise and tenon frames, tongue and groove panels and breadboard ends. Each piece is then hand-sanded and finished to create a rugged-yet-smooth texture that will last for generations.
- Built from solid Pine in a Rustic Grey finish..
- Sand cast metal drawer pulls..
- Felt-lined top drawers..
- Drawers mounted on full-extension ball bearing glides.

Townsend Dresser.description:
The rough and tumble Townsend collection  is crafted from solid hardwood, featuring naturally roughhewn planks with heavy saw marks, pitting and wane.  A 9-step finish uses glaze to highlight wood grain and a light wash to simulate the patina of age. Shallow top drawers are perfect for storing delicate items with the map drawer effect repeated with faux parting rails on large lower drawers. 
- Full-extension ball bearing drawer glides.
- Removable felt liners in the top drawers. 
- Java finish.

Cally Dresser.description:
With graceful curves, modern sensibility and functional appeal, the Cally collection provides an updated take on classic farmhouse style. Crafted entirely from solid pine, rough-hewn planks bear the characteristic saw marks, dents, pits, and random knots of freshly-milled timber. A rugged yet refined Antique Mocha finish uses a rustic glaze to simulate the patina of weathered lumber and a lacquer top coat to showcase the rich natural character of the wood.  
- Built from solid Pine.
- Full-extension ball bearing drawer glides.
- Solid wood drawer boxes constructed using English dovetail joinery are sanded and smoothed to match the exterior finish.
- Cross-banded breadboard top panels.
